page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service via the Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource with a model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the prerequisites.> [!TIP]> Try out the new unified Azure AI Studio (preview) which brings together capabilities from across multiple Azure AI services.
